<http://www.opengis.net/def/crs/EPSG/0/9741_area_of_use> a ns1:AreaOfUse ;
    rdfs:label "United Kingdom (UK) - on or related to the complex of rail routes in the East of Scotland, incorporating the route from Tweedbank through the Borders to Edinburgh; the line from Edinburgh to Aberdeen; routes via Kirkaldy and Cowdenbeath; and routes via Leuchars and Perth to Dundee. "@en ;
